# üåê VPN Configuration Walkthrough

This project demonstrates how to configure a secure VPN using pfSense and OpenVPN. It includes firewall setup, certificate-based authentication, and traffic analysis using Wireshark.

## Tools Used
- pfSense
- OpenVPN
- Wireshark
- Kali Linux (optional)

## Key Concepts
- VPN tunneling and encryption
- Firewall rule configuration
- Certificate-based authentication
- Packet inspection and validation

